claim.claim-text:
1. An endoscope for inspection of an observation cavity, comprising: 
a shaft, said shaft having an inner shaft and an outer shaft, said outer shaft surrounding said inner shaft at a distance; 
an optical system arranged in said inner shaft; 
said shaft being configured in the region of its distal end in such a way that it is substantially impermeable to electromagnetic radiation in the infrared spectral range, wherein said outer shaft at least partially-has, in the region of its distal end, a coating that reflects infrared radiation.
